summary: I keep checking the comments for Captain Marvel and Brie Larson posts cause I need to see positivity for this wonderful creature...
body: I keep checking the comments for Captain Marvel and Brie Larson posts cause I need to see positivity for this wonderful creature of a human being and I don’t know why I’m even surprised that haters go out of their way to insult it. Like you can just not care. Maybe block or filter the tags? I don’t get it.

summary: ‘Captain Marvel’ Goes Higher Further and Faster For the MCU
title: ‘Captain Marvel’ Goes Higher Further and Faster For the MCU
body:
Sorry to burst your bubble, haters, but Captain Marvel is really good.

With all the controversy surrounding Captain Marvel, created by internet trolls, it was refreshing to watch the film and see how wrong they were about it. Captain Marvel has been labeled a feminist film, and it is, but it does so without dragging men down. Instead, the film focuses on women empowerment, sisterhood, and…
